</div>
<div>
<p>春<pc>，</pc>
<measure quantity="1" unit="month">
<num value="1">正</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>
<num value="52">乙卯</num>
<pc>，</pc>募河南北<pc>、</pc>淮南<measure quantity="67" unit="prefectures">
<num value="67">六十七</num>州</measure>兵<pc>，</pc>得<num value="44000">四萬四千</num>餘人<pc>，</pc>詣平壤<pc>、</pc>鏤方行營<pc>。</pc>
